Moss Landing Marine Laboratories (MLML), Moss Landing, California of the California State Universities and Colleges at Fresno, Hayward, Sacramento, San Francisco, San Jose, and Stanislaus.
Five newsletter issues in one entry for 1973.

The Sea Grant newsletter of Moss Landing Marine Laboratories (MLML) in California is published every two months as a free public information service. It contains news of the study and use of the ocean, and emphasizes studies carried on by MLML.
